cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR 

This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with 3D object instance segmentation on point clouds using deep learning. It may also belong to the robotics (cs.RO) sub-category as 3D object instance segmentation is an important task in robotics. Additionally, the paper proposes a novel framework for 3D instance-aware semantic segmentation, which could fall under the machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. Finally, the paper may also be relevant to the graphics (cs.GR) sub-category as it deals with 3D point clouds and their representation.
